description:
Everyone knows that matches are not a toy for children! But our game is an exception to the rule!

Solving puzzles and tasks with matches is an exciting and very useful activity! Such puzzles perfectly train memory, resourcefulness, develop logical thinking, spatial imagination.

The rules of the puzzles are very simple: you need to remove, add or shift a certain number of matches so as to get the correct arithmetic equality, change the outlines or the number of geometric shapes. Solve riddles and keep your mind sharp!

Key features:
• Excellent training for the mind and logic;
• Lots of puzzles of different difficulty levels;
• Management with Joy-Con™️ controllers;
• Relaxing musical accompaniment;
